altername_name: 인터랙티브 멀티 게임 체험판 디스크: 버전 31
name: Interactive Multi-Game Demo Disc Version 31
overview: Interactive Multi Game Demo Disc v31 is a demo and video sampler disc, designed for retail store displays of the Nintendo GameCube. The sampler includes a simple menu and playable demos of Zatch Bell! Mamodo Battles, Super Mario Strikers, Pokémon XD: Gale of Darkness, Mario Superstar Baseball, and The Incredible Hulk: Ultimate Destruction, The disc also features videos of the following: Fire Emblem: Path of Radiance, Dance Dance Revolution: Mario Mix, Pokémon XD: Gale of Darkness, Mario Superstar Baseball, Battalion Wars, SSX on Tour, Ultimate Spider-Man, Viewtiful Joe: Red Hot Rumble, Shadow the Hedgehog, TMNT 3: Mutant Nightmare, WWE Day of Reckoning 2, The Chronicles of Narnia: The Lion, the Witch and the Wardrobe, Nintendogs, the Nintendo DS, and an ESRB ratings video.
